instruction: Make a list of physical activities for a 10-year-old to do.
output:
- Go for a bike ride
- Set up an obstacle course in the backyard
- Go swimming or take a lesson
- Take a family hike
- Play a game of catch
- Plant a garden
- Build and fly a kite
- Build some outdoor crafts
- Have a Nerf battle
- Play board games or card games
- Play hide and seek
- Create an outdoor scavenger hunt
- Run around the neighborhood
